# apex-chromium patch series -- applied in this order by scripts/apply.sh.
#
# These are the RAW .patch files (mid-function edits that a chromium_src overlay
# cannot express). The whole-function overlays in chromium_src/ are applied
# separately by copying, not patching -- see scripts/apply.sh.
#
# Order does not matter here (each patch touches a different file), but the
# series file is the canonical list quilt/apply.sh iterate over.

